snippet.title: Monster Hunter Rise: Sunbreak - Final Digital Event | Developer Roundtable
snippet.description:
Watch the  final Monster Hunter Rise: Sunbreak Digital Event for a look at the Bonus Update, plus a  roundtable disussion with developers as they reflect on the journey of bringing Rise and Sunbreak to life. 

Presented by Monster Hunter series Producer Ryozo Tsujimoto, and Rise and Sunbreak Game Directors Yoshitake Suzuki and Yasunori Ichinose.

Monster Hunter Rise: Sunbreak is available now on Nintendo Switch!
https://bit.ly/MHRiseSB

Start your journey today in Monster Hunter Rise, available now!
